      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 8.986235714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 9.2020862262
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "（けれども突如、日本の第一線を離れてアメリカに移住）\n（以降、ライブバトルには何年も参加していない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（けれども突如、日本の第一線を離れてアメリカに移住）\n（以降、ライブバトルには何年も参加していない）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.2020862262,
      "endTime": 18.3837190311,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "（にも関わらず、圧倒的な累積スコアで君臨し二位の）\n（Baroqueもとうとう記録を抜けないままに引退）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（にも関わらず、圧倒的な累積スコアで君臨し二位の）\n（Baroqueもとうとう記録を抜けないままに引退）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.5995695432,
      "endTime": 27.0511799177,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 27.2670304299
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "あ……ヨーコさんがいるということは\nNexusFesに出演する日本のアイドルって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "あ……ヨーコさんがいるということは\nNexusFesに出演する日本のアイドルって……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.2670304299,
      "endTime": 34.2491164208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 34.464966933
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "speakerNameEn": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-yokboyle001.m4a",
      "text": "そうよ、彼女も出演予定なの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そうよ、彼女も出演予定なの",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.464966933,
      "endTime": 37.6849654596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "speakerNameEn": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-yokboyle002.m4a",
      "text": "日本から、あなたの今のグループも出るとは聞いてるわ\n今日はそのための、敵情視察ってとこかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "日本から、あなたの今のグループも出るとは聞いてるわ\n今日はそのための、敵情視察ってとこかしら？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.8982987404,
      "endTime": 46.7382972717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 46.9316305478
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "speakerNameEn": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-yokboyle003.m4a",
      "text": "……なんてね、冗談よ。ここはアメリカだもの\nVENUSプログラムはないんだから、安心して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……なんてね、冗談よ。ここはアメリカだもの\nVENUSプログラムはないんだから、安心して",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.9316305478,
      "endTime": 54.484964116300006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "彼女が渡米したのは存じてましたが……\nヨーコさんまで一緒だったんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "彼女が渡米したのは存じてましたが……\nヨーコさんまで一緒だったんですね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.6982974688,
      "endTime": 60.0553949038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 60.2712454159
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "speakerNameEn": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-yokboyle004.m4a",
      "text": "歌って踊る以外、何も覚える気がない子なんだもの\n誰かが面倒見なきゃ、すぐに野垂れ死んじゃうわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "歌って踊る以外、何も覚える気がない子なんだもの\n誰かが面倒見なきゃ、すぐに野垂れ死んじゃうわ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.2712454159,
      "endTime": 68.3045799572,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "speakerNameEn": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-yokboyle005.m4a",
      "text": "それに……「みんなを幸せにしたい」って言ってた子を\nこんな業界に引っ張り込んだ、その責任は取らないとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "それに……「みんなを幸せにしたい」って言ってた子を\nこんな業界に引っ張り込んだ、その責任は取らないとね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.5045797665,
      "endTime": 77.97124389,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 78.17124389
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "あの頃……渡米前に、一体彼女に何があったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "あの頃……渡米前に、一体彼女に何があったんですか？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.17124389,
      "endTime": 84.2065487224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 84.4223992346
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "speakerNameEn": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-yokboyle006.m4a",
      "text": "日本にいる頃は、一位、一位と随分持てはやされて\n最初は嬉しそうだったんだけど、だんだん参ってきてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "日本にいる頃は、一位、一位と随分持てはやされて\n最初は嬉しそうだったんだけど、だんだん参ってきてね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.4223992346,
      "endTime": 94.1423964499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "speakerNameEn": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-yokboyle007.m4a",
      "text": "自分に負けて、ステージ裏で泣いてる子を見るのが辛い\n私は誰かを泣かせるために歌ってる訳じゃない、って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "自分に負けて、ステージ裏で泣いてる子を見るのが辛い\n私は誰かを泣かせるために歌ってる訳じゃない、って",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.3557295161,
      "endTime": 103.1157357532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 103.3224022864
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、私は華やかな姿しか知らなかったので\nそんなこととは思わず……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "すみません、私は華やかな姿しか知らなかったので\nそんなこととは思わず……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.3224022864,
      "endTime": 110.2474137305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "speakerNameEn": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-yokboyle008.m4a",
      "text": "隠してたもの、当然よ。……まぁ今は、アメリカに来て\n普通のステージに出る分には、楽しそうにしてるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "隠してたもの、当然よ。……まぁ今は、アメリカに来て\n普通のステージに出る分には、楽しそうにしてるわ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.4632642427,
      "endTime": 119.7499271075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 119.9632601737
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "speakerNameEn": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-yokboyle009.m4a",
      "text": "さて、あなたはそろそろ楽屋に戻った方がいいわよ\n本番前の準備が始まる頃合いだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "さて、あなたはそろそろ楽屋に戻った方がいいわよ\n本番前の準備が始まる頃合いだから",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.9632601737,
      "endTime": 127.4565976142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 127.6632642427
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "speakerNameEn": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-yokboyle010.m4a",
      "text": "それと……藤代さんのことは、残念だったわね\nSundanceは、本当にいいアイドルだったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "それと……藤代さんのことは、残念だったわね\nSundanceは、本当にいいアイドルだったのに",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.6632642427,
      "endTime": 136.9299209276,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "いえ……そう言っていただけるだけで\n葉ちゃんも私も、救われます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "いえ……そう言っていただけるだけで\n葉ちゃんも私も、救われます",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.1299207369,
      "endTime": 143.04527241379998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 143.2611229259
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "speakerNameEn": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-yokboyle011.m4a",
      "text": "ⅢXのステージを、楽しみに観させてもらうわ\nあなたのグループだもの、きっと素敵なんでしょうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ⅢXのステージを、楽しみに観させてもらうわ\nあなたのグループだもの、きっと素敵なんでしょうね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.2611229259,
      "endTime": 150.76111701309998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.0111168224
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　まだkana達が袖にいるのに、映像が始まった\nあー、ステージ前にkana達の紹介入れてるのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ん？　まだkana達が袖にいるのに、映像が始まった\nあー、ステージ前にkana達の紹介入れてるのか",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.0611168224,
      "endTime": 162.4641327221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 158.5068469454
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.6799832343
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "私達、日本じゃ最初から知名度あったし\nいちいち紹介してもらわなくても良かったものねぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "私達、日本じゃ最初から知名度あったし\nいちいち紹介してもらわなくても良かったものねぇ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.6799832343,
      "endTime": 169.9307993888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 170.146649901
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-kor002.m4a",
